OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778839649
OL,3,COnce again Prince Harry shows he's no
OL,4,Clonger prepared to stay silent
OL,6,FGiven he lives on the other side of
OL,7,Fthe Atlantic, should Prince Harry be
OL,8,Fsharing his concerns about
OL,9,Fantisemitism in a country he left six
OL,10,Fyears ago?
OL,12,FAnd did he intend his intervention to
OL,13,Fcoincide, or even clash, with his
OL,14,Ffather's visit to the Jewish community
OL,15,Fin north London?
OL,17,FThey are questions which, perhaps
OL,18,Finevitably, have been raised following
OL,19,Fthe Duke of Sussex's article for the
OL,20,FNew Statesman.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
