PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778839649
OL,3,COnce again Prince Harry shows he's no
OL,4,Clonger prepared to stay silent
OL,6,FWhen we travelled to Ukraine recently
OL,7,Fwith Harry, I asked him about how he
OL,8,Fsees his role on the world stage and
OL,9,Fwhether he now feels freer to speak
OL,10,Fout on sensitive issues.
OL,12,FHe had just made a speech in Kyiv in
OL,13,Fwhich he addressed Russian President
OL,14,FVladimir Putin directly and told the
OL,15,FUSA it needed to show "leadership" on
OL,16,Fthe Ukraine invasion.
OL,18,FHis response was that he didn't want
OL,19,Fto live in a world where people in his
OL,20,Fposition can't speak about "the
OL,21,Frealities that we are seeing".
OL,26,@wD@WOUwD@bO]|D@\OU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778839649
OL,3,COnce again Prince Harry shows he's no
OL,4,Clonger prepared to stay silent
OL,6,FNor did he want to feel "gagged", he
OL,7,Fsaid, just because something is deemed
OL,8,Fto be "political".
OL,10,FThree weeks later, the Prince wrote an
OL,11,Farticle about "a deeply troubling rise
OL,12,Fin antisemitism" in the UK, and
OL,13,Freferred to the recent attacks in
OL,14,FManchester and London.
OL,16,FHe spoke about those in the Jewish
OL,17,Fcommunity who have been "publicly
OL,18,Fcritical of certain state actions", by
OL,19,Fwhich he meant the Israeli military
OL,20,Fstrikes in Gaza and in Lebanon.
OL,26,@nD@YOUnD@`O]pD@GOUpD@QO]zD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
