FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778839649
OL,3,COnce again Prince Harry shows he's no
OL,4,Clonger prepared to stay silent
OL,6,FSo why now?
OL,8,FOn his recent travels, Prince Harry
OL,9,Fmet children in a refugee hospital in
OL,10,FJordan who had been shot, and just a
OL,11,Ffew weeks later, he met those who
OL,12,Fsurvived the Bondi Beach terror attack
OL,13,Fin Sydney.
OL,15,FBoth had a profound effect on him.
OL,17,FHe might be writing now about some
OL,18,Fspecific British examples of
OL,19,Fantisemitism, but he has seen with his
OL,20,Fown eyes how this is a global issue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
