CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778839649
OL,3,COnce again Prince Harry shows he's no
OL,4,Clonger prepared to stay silent
OL,6,FHarry believes he gets to see things
OL,7,Fand meet people that, much like the
OL,8,FRoyal Family he left, give him a
OL,9,Fglobal perspective that few others get.
OL,11,FOf course, he was born and raised in
OL,12,FBritain and is still a prince in the
OL,13,Fline of succession of the British
OL,14,FRoyal Family, and therefore, he will
OL,15,Foften see things from a British
OL,16,Fperspective, despite living in
OL,17,FCalifornia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
