PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778839649
OL,3,COnce again Prince Harry shows he's no
OL,4,Clonger prepared to stay silent
OL,6,FGiven he is not Jewish, nor Muslim and
OL,7,Fgiven that he doesn't live in the
OL,8,FMiddle East, his detractors will say
OL,9,Fhe should not have a platform to speak
OL,10,Fon issues such as this, and perhaps he
OL,11,Fshould stick to areas like the
OL,12,Fmilitary or veterans where he does
OL,13,Fhave some lived experience.
OL,15,FBut inasmuch as his home is a Royal
OL,16,FCourt in Montecito, the Duke of Sussex
OL,17,Fhas concluded that staying silent is
OL,18,Fthe wrong choice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
