CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778839649
OL,3,COnce again Prince Harry shows he's no
OL,4,Clonger prepared to stay silent
OL,6,FHarry doesn't want to stand on the
OL,7,Fedge of the football pitch with no
OL,8,Fvoice; he wants to be one of the
OL,9,Fplayers showing others what he can do,
OL,10,Fwhat he has been told and what he has
OL,11,Fseen.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FDid he try to overshadow King Charles'
OL,19,Fvisit to Golders Green?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
