FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778839649
OL,3,COnce again Prince Harry shows he's no
OL,4,Clonger prepared to stay silent
OL,6,FNo more than the Princess of Wales did
OL,7,Fby having engagements in Italy on the
OL,8,Fsame day as the King's visit.
OL,10,FSenior staff in Harry's office say
OL,11,Fthey were not aware of the King's
OL,12,Fvisit to see the victims of the recent
OL,13,Fattack, as it had not been announced
OL,14,Fin advance.
OL,16,FSo, just like we saw in Ukraine,
OL,17,FPrince Harry is done with being silent.
OL,19,FIn his view, being silent does not
OL,20,Fmake the problem go away.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
